WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.266 --> 00:00:01.401
♪♪

00:00:02.535 --> 00:00:05.471 line:0%
<i> Your brain is like
 a hungry sponge.</i>

00:00:05.504 --> 00:00:08.074 line:0%
<i> It's constantly absorbing
 information.</i>

00:00:08.707 --> 00:00:12.178 line:0%
What are we saying
by raising an eyebrow?

00:00:13.279 --> 00:00:16.416 line:0%
<i> What matters more,
 being right or fitting in?</i>

00:00:17.183 --> 00:00:21.021 line:0%
<i> Why is it that we love
 destroying things?</i>

00:00:22.455 --> 00:00:23.289 line:0%
Ahh!

00:00:23.322 --> 00:00:25.792 line:0%
♪♪

00:00:25.825 --> 00:00:26.559 line:0%
Why?

00:00:26.592 --> 00:00:30.163 line:0%
♪♪

00:00:30.196 --> 00:00:31.230 line:0%
<i> Our lives are full</i>

00:00:31.263 --> 00:00:32.398 line:0%
<i> of decisions that we think</i>

00:00:32.431 --> 00:00:34.067 line:0%
<i> we make of our own
 free will,</i>

00:00:34.100 --> 00:00:35.001 line:0%
<i> but do we?</i>

00:00:35.035 --> 00:00:36.736 line:0%
<i> It can tell me
 what I was going to do</i>

00:00:36.769 --> 00:00:38.838 line:0%
before I know I was going
to do it.

00:00:38.871 --> 00:00:40.440 line:0%
- What?!
- Yeah.

00:00:40.840 --> 00:00:43.176 line:0%
Psychologists say that
fewer than three days

00:00:43.209 --> 00:00:45.478 line:0%
in a room like this
can lead to brain damage.

00:00:45.511 --> 00:00:47.147 line:0%
<i> I will be staying
 in this room...</i>

00:00:48.214 --> 00:00:49.282 line:0%
for three days.

00:00:49.315 --> 00:00:51.451 line:0%
♪♪

00:00:51.484 --> 00:00:53.653 line:0%
I am so confused.

00:00:54.353 --> 00:00:55.822 line:0%
<i> Your brain can be useful.</i>

00:00:55.855 --> 00:00:57.423 line:0%
Oh, my God!

00:00:57.456 --> 00:00:58.624 line:0%
<i> It can be dangerous.</i>

00:00:58.657 --> 00:00:59.692 line:0%
[grunting]

00:00:59.725 --> 00:01:00.560 line:0%
[laughing]

00:01:00.593 --> 00:01:01.661 line:0%
<i> And it can be...</i>

00:01:01.694 --> 00:01:03.096 line:0%
<i> a lot of fun.</i>

00:01:03.129 --> 00:01:12.372 line:0%
♪♪

